1
00:00:52,830 --> 00:00:53,860
Madman.

2
00:00:54,800 --> 00:00:57,060
Do you know how dangerous it was just now?

3
00:00:57,830 --> 00:00:59,200
If discovered,

4
00:01:00,430 --> 00:01:03,560
Helan Ci will slice you into a thousand pieces tomorrow.

5
00:01:03,800 --> 00:01:04,830
I don't care.

6
00:01:06,060 --> 00:01:06,930
I only know

7
00:01:08,360 --> 00:01:10,160
you didn't push me away just now.

8
00:01:17,360 --> 00:01:18,300
Qu Jingzhi,

9
00:01:18,730 --> 00:01:20,400
listen clearly to me.

10
00:01:21,330 --> 00:01:22,660
The one you just kissed

11
00:01:23,230 --> 00:01:25,430
is a bloodstained eunuch.

12
00:01:25,930 --> 00:01:27,460
In this man-eating palace,

13
00:01:27,830 --> 00:01:29,760
your ridiculous sincerity is not needed.

14
00:01:29,760 --> 00:01:31,560
Put away your wishful thinking.

15
00:01:31,730 --> 00:01:33,960
Don't come and taint me with your bad luck.

16
00:01:33,960 --> 00:01:35,560
Whether it's sincere or not,

17
00:01:36,229 --> 00:01:37,400
I have the final say.

18
00:01:38,200 --> 00:01:39,130
Ying Wujiu,

19
00:01:40,160 --> 00:01:42,360
don't even think about pushing me away again.

20
00:01:42,360 --> 00:01:43,460
If you dare to die,

21
00:01:44,530 --> 00:01:47,460
I will go to the underworld and snatch your soul back.

22
00:02:04,460 --> 00:02:05,600
Your Majesty.

23
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:07,430
During the thunderstorm last night,

24
00:02:07,430 --> 00:02:09,630
I was ordered to patrol the long street.

25
00:02:10,960 --> 00:02:11,930
I vaguely saw

26
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:15,660
the figure of the Director of the Eastern Depot.

27
00:02:15,730 --> 00:02:16,530
Oh.

28
00:02:18,060 --> 00:02:19,660
In the pouring rain,

29
00:02:21,560 --> 00:02:24,760
this castrated dog wasn't staying in the Guard Division.

30
00:02:25,530 --> 00:02:27,560
What was he doing running to the long street?

31
00:02:27,560 --> 00:02:28,630
I am incompetent.

32
00:02:29,030 --> 00:02:30,730
My eyes were blinded by the wind and rain.

33
00:02:30,730 --> 00:02:31,530
It's just that

34
00:02:32,329 --> 00:02:33,160
Her Ladyship

35
00:02:33,930 --> 00:02:36,560
also seemed to be on the same long street last night,

36
00:02:36,560 --> 00:02:38,220
taking shelter from the rain.

37
00:02:38,600 --> 00:02:41,960
The two seemed to have a brief encounter.

38
00:02:45,360 --> 00:02:46,300
Encounter?

39
00:02:48,829 --> 00:02:50,829
He's a rootless slave,

40
00:02:51,400 --> 00:02:53,230
not even a man.

41
00:02:53,730 --> 00:02:55,960
Does he deserve to encounter my woman?

42
00:02:58,329 --> 00:02:59,930
Pass on my decree.

43
00:03:00,360 --> 00:03:02,420
Move to the royal martial arts arena.

44
00:03:02,900 --> 00:03:05,030
Tell Ying Wujiu to roll over and see me.

45
00:03:05,200 --> 00:03:07,130
I want to see with my own eyes

46
00:03:07,130 --> 00:03:10,630
whether this knife has developed a rebellious bone.

47
00:03:17,800 --> 00:03:18,660
Your Ladyship.

48
00:03:18,700 --> 00:03:22,930
The Emperor requests you to immediately go to the royal martial arts arena to accompany him.

49
00:03:22,930 --> 00:03:23,500
Got it.

50
00:03:25,200 --> 00:03:28,130
Why is the Emperor in the mood to go to the arena today?

51
00:03:28,160 --> 00:03:30,130
The Emperor is in good health today.

52
00:03:30,130 --> 00:03:34,130
He is competing in archery with Director Ying of the Eastern Depot in the arena.

53
00:03:34,130 --> 00:03:35,829
He said to let you go

54
00:03:36,600 --> 00:03:37,660
to liven things up.

55
00:03:41,200 --> 00:03:42,530
Helan Ci is suspicious.

56
00:03:43,329 --> 00:03:44,530
He is trying to test me

57
00:03:44,760 --> 00:03:47,020
and even more so to humiliate Ying Wujiu.

58
00:03:51,560 --> 00:03:54,200
Let's go. Don't keep the Emperor waiting.

59
00:04:11,700 --> 00:04:13,630
The Emperor's archery is godlike.

60
00:04:13,630 --> 00:04:16,430
But the Director is the Emperor's sharpest knife.

61
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:18,399
Using him as a target

62
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:19,930
is a bit of a waste of talent.

63
00:04:19,930 --> 00:04:21,899
No matter how sharp the knife is,

64
00:04:21,899 --> 00:04:23,400
if it develops a rebellious bone

65
00:04:23,400 --> 00:04:25,900
or covets what it shouldn't covet,

66
00:04:25,900 --> 00:04:27,330
then it's just a piece of scrap iron.

67
00:04:27,330 --> 00:04:30,860
Ying Wujiu, since you are my slave,

68
00:04:30,900 --> 00:04:34,900
then put an apple on your head to liven things up for my medicinal primer.

69
00:04:40,530 --> 00:04:41,460
Don't be afraid.

70
00:04:43,900 --> 00:04:45,900
I will never let you die again.

71
00:04:48,330 --> 00:04:49,159
Are you crazy?

72
00:04:49,159 --> 00:04:50,930
For a eunuch,

73
00:04:51,330 --> 00:04:54,460
you dare to block my black iron hook with your bare hands.

74
00:04:54,860 --> 00:04:55,900
Call the imperial physician.

75
00:04:55,900 --> 00:04:57,700
If there is a single scar left on her hand,

76
00:04:57,700 --> 00:04:59,330
I will bury the entire Imperial Hospital with her.

77
00:04:59,330 --> 00:05:00,990
You hurt yourself to save him.

78
00:05:01,230 --> 00:05:01,930
Good.

79
00:05:01,930 --> 00:05:02,930
Qu Jingzhi,

80
00:05:02,930 --> 00:05:04,300
I will make you see clearly today.

81
00:05:04,300 --> 00:05:05,600
As long as I'm not tired of you,

82
00:05:05,600 --> 00:05:06,600
you are mine in life,

83
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:07,400
and mine in death.

84
00:05:07,400 --> 00:05:08,760
He is a castrated dog who isn't even a man.

85
00:05:08,760 --> 00:05:10,330
How can he compete with me?

86
00:05:11,500 --> 00:05:12,430
Commander Ying,

87
00:05:12,700 --> 00:05:14,230
Qu Jingzhi was at the training ground today.

88
00:05:14,230 --> 00:05:14,960
To save you,

89
00:05:14,960 --> 00:05:16,300
she was seriously injured.

90
00:05:16,300 --> 00:05:17,500
My heart aches for her.

91
00:05:17,500 --> 00:05:17,860
Tonight,

92
00:05:17,860 --> 00:05:20,530
I am bestowing upon her this red peacock gauze dress from the Western Regions.

93
00:05:20,530 --> 00:05:22,300
You are my most trusted servant.
